  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.9.5">
<l>tīyem perumāṉ nīrem perumāṉ ticaiyu mirunilaṉu</l>
<l>māyem perumā ṉāki niṉṟā laṭiyōṅ kāṇōmāl</l>
<l>tāyem perumāṉ tantai tantai yāvī raṭiyōmuk</l>
<l>kēyem perumā ṉallī rōnī rinta ḷūrīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Fire is our lord; water is our lord. If our lord remains</l>
<l>As the directions and the vast lands, we devotees cannot see him at all.</l>
<l>Our lord is [our] mother. You who are our father’s father,</l>
<l>You of Intaḷūr, are you not the lord to us, your devotees?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
